{"url":"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/staff/post-5203","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"ja\">\n<head>\n<title>趣味のマラソンから…！&#x1f3c3; | アルプ薬局 ブログ</title>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1\">\n\n<!-- All in One SEO Pack 2.3.12 by Michael Torbert of Semper Fi Web Design[40,79] -->\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/staff/post-5203\" />\n<!-- /all in one seo pack -->\n<link rel='dns-prefetch' href='//ajax.googleapis.com' />\n<link rel='dns-prefetch' href='//s.w.org' />\n<link rel='stylesheet' id='style-css'  href='https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/style.css?ver=4.7.3' type='text/css' media='all' />\n<script type='text/javascript' src='http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.min.js?ver=4.7.3'></script>\n<link rel='shortlink' href='https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/?p=5203' />\n\n<link rel=\"pingback\" href=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/xmlrpc.php\">\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"//fonts.googleapis.com/earlyaccess/notosansjapanese.css\">\n<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/earlyaccess/mplus1p.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" />\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/js/touch.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/js/tabmenu.js\"></script>\n<link rel=\"apple-touch-icon-precomposed\" href=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/img/webclip.png\" />\n<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/img/alp.ico\">\n<!--[if lt IE 9]>\n<script src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/js/respond.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/js/html5.js\"></script>\n<![endif]-->\n\n</head>\n\n<body>\n\t\n<!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->\n<script async src=\"https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-Y3YBPRXKL3\"></script>\n<script>\n  window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];\n  function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}\n  gtag('js', new Date());\n\n  gtag('config', 'G-Y3YBPRXKL3');\n</script>\n<div id=\"wrapper\">\n\n<header id=\"site-header\" role=\"banner\">\n\t\n\n<div class=\"site-title\"><h1><a href=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp\" rel=\"home\"><img src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/img/logo.png\" width=\"180\"  alt=\"アルプ薬局\"></a></h1></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"blog-title\"><h2>スタッフブログ</h2></div>\n<div class=\"blog-title2\"><p>アルプスタッフがつぶやく、日々の徒然日記</p></div><div class=\"blog-title-img\"><img src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/img/alp-blog-01.jpg\"></div>\n\n\n\n\n</header>\n\n<div id=\"content\">   \n\n\t<div class=\"post\"> \n<div class=\"post-single\">\n\t\t\n\t\t<div id=\"breadcrumb\">\n        <span class=\"bread\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://data-vocabulary.org/Breadcrumb\"><a href=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/\" itemprop=\"url\"><span itemprop=\"title\">TOP</span> </a></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<span class=\"bread\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://data-vocabulary.org/Breadcrumb\"> <a href=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/category/staff\" itemprop=\"url\"><span itemprop=\"title\">スタッフブログ</span></a></span>\t\t</div>\n\n\n<article itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Article\" role=\"main\">\n\n<header>\n<h1 itemprop=\"headline\">趣味のマラソンから…！&#x1f3c3;</h1>\n<div class=\"align-right\"><p><i class=\"fa fa-calendar\"></i> <time itemprop=\"datePublished\" datetime=\"2026-06-05T00:00:33+00:00\">2026/06/05</time></p></div>\n</header>\n\n\n<div itemprop=\"articleBody\">\n<p><b>妻</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">と</span><span style=\"color: #ff6600\"><b>趣味</b></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">で始めた</span><span style=\"color: #0000ff\"><b>マラソン</b></span><b>&#x1f3c3;</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">が</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">今年で</span><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><b>「3年」</b></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">を</span><span style=\"color: #000000\"><b>経過</b></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">しました</span><b>！</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#x1f44f;&#x1f38a;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">今年は</span><span style=\"color: #008000\"><b>新潟ハーフマラソン</b></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">に出場し、</span><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><b>1時間30分14秒</b></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">で</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">記録を</span><span style=\"color: #0000ff\"><b>更新</b></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">しました&#x1f60a;&#x1f389;</span></p>\n<p><strong>週4回</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">くらいのペースで</span><b><span style=\"color: #ff0000\">1日11キロ</span>&#x1f3c3;</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">走っていたので</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">今回は</span><span style=\"color: #ff6600\"><b>自信</b></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">がありました&#x1f601;&#x1f44d;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">その<strong>勢い</strong>&#x1f525;で出場した</span><span style=\"color: #008080\"><b>柏崎潮風マラソン(フル)&#x1f3c3;</b></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">で</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><b><span style=\"color: #ff6600\">3時間40分10秒</span><span style=\"color: #000000\">記録更新</span></b></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">とはなりませんでした&#x1f61e;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">やはり</span><span style=\"color: #0000ff\"><b>ハーフマラソン</b></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">と</span><span style=\"color: #008000\"><b>フルマラソン</b></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">では</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #008000\"><b>練習方法</b></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">が</span><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><b>全く別物</b></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">だと</span><strong>実感</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">させられた大会となりました&#x1f440;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">今年は</span><span style=\"color: #3366ff\"><b>新潟シティマラソン&#x1f3c3;</b></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">に出場予定なので、</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">そこに</span><strong><span style=\"color: #ff6600\">コンディション</span></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">を持っていけるように</span><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000\">頑張ります</span></strong><b>&#x1f601;&#x1f525;</b></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-5194\" src=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/gmail_images20260519_152502-1-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/gmail_images20260519_152502-1-225x300.jpg 225w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/gmail_images20260519_152502-1.jpg 675w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" />　 <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-5193\" src=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/gmail_images20260519_152413-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/gmail_images20260519_152413-225x300.jpg 225w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/gmail_images20260519_152413.jpg 675w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-5192\" src=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1gmail_images20260519_151948-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1gmail_images20260519_151948-225x300.jpg 225w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1gmail_images20260519_151948.jpg 675w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">新潟支社　T</span></p>\n<div class=\"blog-alp-logo\"><img src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/img/alp-logo.jpg\" width=\"130\" alt=\"アルプ薬局\"></div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n